{"tid":616780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來港珠澳人工島早在2016年已經散咗","createTime":"2018-04-04T12:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T15:51:45.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb6962fb1754d90db3262c91eb0904a581123e1d","tid":616780,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋連接海底隧道的東人工島，近日被航拍發燒友意外拍到防波堤疑似被海浪沖散，並出現大範圍「崩角」。事件被香港傳媒廣泛報道，引起關注。香港路政署回應傳媒指，該路段為內地水域，因此拒絕回應工程是否出現失誤；而內地港珠澳大橋管理局則在網頁上回覆，指控港媒為不實報導，「被誤傳『海浪沖散』的兩個部位，經過長期的觀測，分析以及『天鴿』颱風襲擊後的觀測，並無受到任何影響，完全滿足相關規範規定及設計要求」，並指防波堤的扭工字塊，設計標高在水平面以下，更按要求採取「隨機擺放」，否認被海浪沖散。<br />\n<br />\n翻查2016年4月人工島興建圖片，原來「崩角」早已存在，但是為何要這樣設計，真是一個謎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkplanninginfo/photos/a.132297946965141.1073741829.131455797049356/809655769229352/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkplanninginfo%2Fphotos%2Fa.132297946965141.1073741829.131455797049356%2F809655769229352%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2BtdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a79771a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkplanninginfo/photos/a.132297946965141.1073741829.131455797049356/809655769229352/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年4月<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/203305_862415509827cc8ca4d39acd418751ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F203305_862415509827cc8ca4d39acd418751ae.jpg&h=76f649fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《新華社》2017年7月5日拍攝的相片<br />\n<strong><a href=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2040000/2043979/FtXueDdrp7eZbY6HYw5_58WcGvA_YgzNoK-IM6CviDM_600.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2040000%2F2043979%2FFtXueDdrp7eZbY6HYw5_58WcGvA_YgzNoK-IM6CviDM_600.jpg&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2BtdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e502d5ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2040000/2043979/FtXueDdrp7eZbY6HYw5_58WcGvA_YgzNoK-IM6CviDM_600.jpg</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n2017年11月<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2040000/2043979/1_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2040000%2F2043979%2F1_600.jpeg&h=a32e818d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月航拍發燒友Waichiu Wong在網上發布的相片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2040000/2043979/2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2040000%2F2043979%2F2_600.jpg&h=73ea55ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20193eb346bc4f0e6fd6a685c9e70805c782cf05","tid":616780,"uid":12241,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"密集式恐懼<br />\n拎個DESIGN TEAM出黎祭旗啦<br />\n香港班仆街consultant D垃圾DESIGN流撚到爆<br />\n搵呢D石做防玻堤咪即係同D警犬拎個紙皮塞住條水喉一撚樣"},{"pid":"7e94e54098691bf4b68185c98d54ad81574a934b","tid":616780,"uid":115525,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bb6962fb1754d90db3262c91eb0904a581123e1d","tid":616780,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋連接海底隧道的東人工島，近日被航拍發燒友意外拍到防波堤疑似被海浪沖散，並出現大範圍「崩角」。事件被香港傳媒廣泛報道，引起關注。香港路政署回應傳媒指，該路段為內地水域，因此拒絕回應工程是否出現失誤；而內地港珠澳大橋管理局則在網頁上回覆，指控港媒為不實報導，「被誤傳『海浪沖散』的兩個部位，經過長期的觀測，分析以及『天鴿』颱風襲擊後的觀測，並無受到任何影響，完全滿足相關規範規定及設計要求」，並指防波堤的扭工字塊，設計標高在水平面以下，更按要求採取「隨機擺放」，否認被海浪沖散。<br />\n<br />\n翻查2016年4月人工島興建圖片，原來「崩角」早已存在，但是為何要這樣設計，真是一個謎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkplanninginfo/photos/a.132297946965141.1073741829.131455797049356/809655769229352/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkplanninginfo%2Fphotos%2Fa.132297946965141.1073741829.131455797049356%2F809655769229352%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2BtdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a797